text: No matter the situation or circumstance? I know there’s a lot I need to deal with but I will make it a point to not make it an issue. My disability won’t be an excuse. Just understand what my symptoms are & my limitations. If u don’t… it’s not my problem

author: Becks Amillion
text: That’s not very supportive. I know it’s not but being the natural part of me causes conflict. I want the VERY BEST for everyone I encounter. Should I still want the best for those same ppl when they….? Should I want the best for them?

author: Becks Amillion
text: I know my update took longer. I am doing better. There’s just a lot of truths I need to come to terms with. Those same truths is thinking” Didn’t I say this shyt?“ I’m learning how to be supportive without being supportive.

author: Becks Amillion
text: They won’t be in the place I started from. They will be more informed & have so much more at their disposal. I believe in this bcuz my oldest is the proof. I may not know a lot but best believe… my old, modest, conservative ass know enough.

author: Becks Amillion
text: Cont’d… Don’t get anything. One day we will get on the same page. They will understand. I have a picture that has been engraved in my mind for how I hope things will go for my sons. Only the oldest knows what I’m trying to do & what I’ve already put in place

author: Becks Amillion
text: I also didn’t know I was as toxic as I am. I have a lot of issues that I say I’m over but I’m not. I am who I am. Flaws & all. I’m working on me. I’m working on so many things that mean so much to me. The one thing I thought had an understanding with…
